java.lang.Object
  ch.uzh.ddis.katts.query.AbstractNode

public abstract class AbstractNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements Node

The AbstractNode implements some convenient methods for nodes. It provides functionality to link the different nodes together with their streams and to init the different node implementation.

Author:
Thomas Hunziker
